00:48:19,220 --> 00:48:20,950
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}Call your first witness.

750
00:48:21,030 --> 00:48:25,790
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}So, Mr. Klauss Vanderhayden of Honey Farms, big company you have.

751
00:48:25,860 --> 00:48:27,200
