00:48:37,610 --> 00:48:41,550
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}I don't imagine you employ any bee-free-ers, do you?

756
00:48:41,610 --> 00:48:43,550
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}No. I couldn't hear you.

757
00:48:43,620 --> 00:48:44,950
