00:48:56,290 --> 00:48:59,820
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}Yogi Bear, Fozzie Bear, Build-A-Bear.

762
00:48:59,900 --> 00:49:01,230
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}You mean like this?

