00:51:14,300 --> 00:51:19,360
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}No, I was just late. I tried to call, but... the battery.

804
00:51:19,440 --> 00:51:23,700
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}I didn't want all this to go to waste, so I called Barry. Luckily, he was free.

