00:51:24,440 --> 00:51:26,770
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}Oh, that was lucky.

806
00:51:29,110 --> 00:51:31,910
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}There's a little left. I could heat it up.

