00:51:46,460 --> 00:51:50,460
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}That's where I usually sit. Right... there.

811
00:51:52,140 --> 00:51:55,400
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}Ken, Barry was looking at your resume,

