00:52:54,870 --> 00:52:56,330
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}A lot of ads.

828
00:52:56,400 --> 00:52:59,670
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}Remember what Van said, why is your life more valuable than mine?

