00:54:15,780 --> 00:54:17,650
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}We need to talk!

846
00:54:17,720 --> 00:54:19,650
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}He's just a little bee!

847
00:54:19,720 --> 00:54:24,710
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}And he happens to be the nicest bee I've met in a long time!

848
00:54:24,790 --> 00:54:30,060
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}Long time? What are you talking about? ! Are there other bugs in your life?

