00:54:30,130 --> 00:54:35,070
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}No, but there are other things bugging me in life. And you're one of them!

850
00:54:35,130 --> 00:54:38,070
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}Fine! Talking bees, no yogurt night...

851
00:54:38,140 --> 00:54:42,400
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}My nerves are fried from riding on this emotional roller coaster!

