00:55:07,200 --> 00:55:09,860
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}I couldn't overcome it. Oh, well.

859
00:55:09,930 --> 00:55:11,770
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}Are you OK for the trial?

