01:06:50,430 --> 01:06:52,460
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}So if there's no more pollination,

1048
01:06:52,540 --> 01:06:55,330
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}it could all just go south here, couldn't it?

