01:07:02,880 --> 01:07:05,040
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}How about a suicide pact?

1051
01:07:05,120 --> 01:07:06,640
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}How do we do it?

1052
01:07:06,720 --> 01:07:09,710
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}I'll sting you, you step on me. That just kills you twice.

1053
01:07:09,790 --> 01:07:11,120
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}Right, right.

1054
01:07:11,720 --> 01:07:16,060
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}Listen, Barry... sorry, but I gotta get going.

1055
01:07:22,800 --> 01:07:25,890
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}I had to open my mouth and talk.

1056
01:07:27,910 --> 01:07:29,240
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}Vanessa?

1057
01:07:32,080 --> 01:07:35,170
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}Vanessa? Why are you leaving? Where are you going?

1058
01:07:35,250 --> 01:07:38,270
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}To the final Tournament of Roses parade in Pasadena.

1059
01:07:38,350 --> 01:07:42,290
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}They've moved it to this weekend because all the flowers are dying.

1060
01:07:42,350 --> 01:07:45,790
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}It's the last chance I'll ever have to see it.

1061
01:07:45,860 --> 01:07:50,320
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}Vanessa, I just wanna say I'm sorry. I never meant it to turn out like this.

