01:08:43,080 --> 01:08:45,010
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}I thought maybe you were remodeling.

1081
01:08:45,080 --> 01:08:49,350
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}But I have another idea, and it's greater than my previous ideas combined.

1082
01:08:49,420 --> 01:08:51,220
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}I don't want to hear it!

1083
01:08:52,160 --> 01:08:56,150
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}All right, they have the roses, the roses have the pollen.

