01:08:56,230 --> 01:08:59,420
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}I know every bee, plant and flower bud in this park.

1085
01:08:59,500 --> 01:09:03,090
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}All we gotta do is get what they've got back here with what we've got.

1086
01:09:03,170 --> 01:09:04,290
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}Bees. Park.

1087
01:09:04,370 --> 01:09:05,530
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}Pollen! Flowers.

