01:09:12,240 --> 01:09:15,230
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}They've got nothing but flowers, floats and cotton candy.

1091
01:09:15,310 --> 01:09:16,610
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}Security will be tight.

