01:09:16,680 --> 01:09:18,440
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}I have an idea.

1093
01:09:18,520 --> 01:09:19,980
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}Vanessa Bloome, FTD.

1094
01:09:20,050 --> 01:09:22,710
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}Official floral business. It's real.

