01:09:22,790 --> 01:09:25,190
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}Sorry, ma'am. Nice brooch.

1096
01:09:25,260 --> 01:09:26,920
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}Thank you. It was a gift.

1097
01:09:27,860 --> 01:09:30,690
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}Once inside, we just pick the right float.

1098
01:09:31,700 --> 01:09:33,860
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}How about The Princess and the Pea?

1099
01:09:33,930 --> 01:09:36,870
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}I could be the princess, and you could be the pea!

1100
01:09:36,930 --> 01:09:38,200
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}Yes, I got it.

1101
01:09:40,040 --> 01:09:42,300
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}Where should I sit? What are you?

1102
01:09:42,370 --> 01:09:44,240
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}I believe I'm the pea. The pea?

1103
01:09:44,310 --> 01:09:45,970
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}It goes under the mattresses.

1104
01:09:46,040 --> 01:09:48,810
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}Not in this fairy tale, sweetheart. I'm getting the marshal.

