01:09:48,880 --> 01:09:51,870
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}You do that! This whole parade is a fiasco!

1106
01:09:54,150 --> 01:09:55,950
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}Let's see what this baby'll do.

