01:10:42,470 --> 01:10:43,560
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}It's got to work.

1121
01:10:43,630 --> 01:10:46,260
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}Attention, passengers, this is Captain Scott.

1122
01:10:46,340 --> 01:10:48,630
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}We have a bit of bad weather in New York.

