{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}Vanessa, this is nothing more than a big metal bee.

1154
01:12:30,410 --> 01:12:32,430
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}It's got giant wings, huge engines.

1155
01:12:32,510 --> 01:12:33,810
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}I can't fly a plane.

1156
01:12:33,880 --> 01:12:36,210
{\fncambria\fs22\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\3c&H000000&\i1}Why not? Isn't John Travolta a pilot? Yes.

